In-person sessions grant the opportunity to meet face-to-face with your counselor. If you select this option, all Covid-19 health protocols will be observed.

Mondays, Wednesdays, Fridays

Virtual Counseling uses a secure platform to protect your information while providing the same quality services you would receive if at a face-to-face session.

Mondays, Wednesdays, Fridays

Every 2nd and 4th Saturday ONLY VIRTUAL

Cancellations made without 24hrs notice will incur a fee.

We use Zoom for all virtual sessions and will appreciate that you use your camera.

SCROLL BELOW TO SELECT BOOKING DATES

Starting is often the most challenging part, but we are here to ensure it's easy and stress-free for everyone.

A consultation is a chance for us to connect before starting therapy. The primary goal of this meeting is to help you decide if you are ready to schedule your initial session.

During your Free Virtual consultation session, our Client Coordination team will ensure that you feel listened to, understood, and supported. At SPFLEC, this optional 20-minute virtual conversation is available. If you prefer, you can go ahead and book your first counseling or coaching session without this step.
